title: Richard Bandler - Art of Amnesia & Negation
description:
Richard Bandler - Art of Amnesia & Negation
Self-help | 1CD | MP3 128 Kbps | 33 Mb
Language: English


Do you have something you want to forget....but continue to remember?!


Most people find it easier to remember things they should forget and forget the things they should remember.

On this CD, Richard Bandler takes a highly-entertaining journey into the realms of Amnesia - the healing phenomenon and the subtle art of negation.

While clearly demonstrating and teaching the subject at a conscious level, Richard Bandler also provides some marvellous unconscious surprises!

Recorded at the One Year Training Programme in London 1997, this is Richard Bandler at his very best ...
